@startuml

[*] -> Registration : Start Registration Process
Registration -> RegistrationFailed : Registration Fails
RegistrationFailed -> Registration : Retry Registration
RegistrationFailed -> Login : Go to Login
Login -> SignedIn : User Signs In
SignedIn -> FacilitiesAccess : Access Available Facilities
FacilitiesAccess -> ReadContent : Read News and Expert Content
ReadContent -> SymptomCheck : Check Symptoms or Use Fitness Checking Options
SymptomCheck -> ContinueSession : Continue Using System
SymptomCheck -> EndSession : Finish Session
ContinueSession -> PaymentProcessing : Process Payment for Services
PaymentProcessing -> InsuranceValidation : Validate Insurance for Finance-Related Services
InsuranceValidation -> CashPayment : Choose Cash Payment Method
CashPayment -> CashDetails : Inform About Cash Payment Details
CashPayment -> InsurancePayment : Complete Insurance-Based Payments
InsurancePayment -> EndSession : Finish Session
SignedIn -> FeedbackCollection : Collect User Feedback After Service Completion
EndSession -> Logout : Log Out Users

@enduml
